caption: *cue long paragraph* I want to thank Jack and Jack for always being there for me and helping me through so much crap in my life, and one day, hopefully, I'll get the chance to FINALLY meet them. I've been waiting for such a long time and I know that this is, like, my only chance and I am taking it. Jack and Jack can always ligthen my mood, and make me happy. Me, being a teenager who lives in Iceland, always creating scenarios in my head about the jacks and I meeting. This opportunity could be my last and that's why I really want to win. #contest
